Class Folder

  • java.lang.Object
    • businesslogic.Folder

  • public class Folder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the folder object.

    Exactly like a file explorer, a folder is composed of files and other folders. Here files are images.

    A folder is characteristic by:

    • A name
    • A parent folder
    • A list of folder
    • A list of images
